{"tid":1721080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【出現了】習近平：香港持續發生的激進暴力犯罪行為，嚴重踐踏法治和社會秩序；止暴制亂、恢復秩序是香港當前最緊迫的任務。","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:47.000Z","uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5b9f28a64ed12a2104f832bc8d4e2b32d78aa9","tid":1721080,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"習近平：堅定支持行政長官依法施政 香港警方嚴正執法<br />\n2019-11-14 HKT 22:16<br />\n 分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n國家主席習近平表示，將繼續堅定支持行政長官帶領香港特別行政區政府依法施政，堅定支持香港警方嚴正執法，堅定支持香港司法機構依法懲治暴力犯罪分子。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在巴西利亞出席金磚國家領導人第十一次會晤時指出，中國政府維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的決心堅定不移，貫徹「一國兩制」方針的決心堅定不移，反對任何外部勢力干涉香港事務的決心堅定不移。<br />\n<br />\n習近平提到，香港持續發生的激進暴力犯罪行為，嚴重踐踏法治和社會秩序，嚴重破壞香港繁榮穩定，嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是香港當前最緊迫的任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492242-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492242-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc60XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=23f3962b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492242-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=960105b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492242-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左見林鄭果次<br />\n今次係習近平第一次親自對抗爭表態"},{"pid":"85997d4ebef821568e07b26eb87adca332544a1a","tid":1721080,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae6c17c6e75324e0125b1b06d83c5c1d7a20b3df","tid":1721080,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2IcJPwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2IcJPwF.jpg&h=4a8b47dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f618d56fc67d5cab8f8c1bf28198b73e2649451b","tid":1721080,"uid":307998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"林奠：香港唔係自治<br />\n<br />\n邊個嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線？"},{"pid":"55d6bd7084d11db39dbd963294ea97fdcf4f079e","tid":1721080,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"超鄧趕毛，六四2.0<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"41bfe2bdba2a8bf89ceb58d89a80a0187f9aa6de","tid":1721080,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"搵文宣手足譯做英文"},{"pid":"e58a91ffb1c9150f459939568fbca0078c0ce9f6","tid":1721080,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"習大大訓教啦，香港市民關心你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cc92842a7c722558be3faf0993b5f0a31d2cd1","tid":1721080,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"9a93074a6ae08b59fd9694dd6576fc8ecd6756bc","tid":1721080,"uid":23373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"幾時出解放軍收popo皮?"},{"pid":"3d0eb5c00c1c0e134deee99a2bd05518220cfbcb","tid":1721080,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a93074a6ae08b59fd9694dd6576fc8ecd6756bc","tid":1721080,"uid":23373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"幾時出解放軍收popo皮?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"將繼續堅定支持行政長官帶領香港特別行政區政府依法施政，堅定支持香港警方嚴正執法，堅定支持香港司法機構依法懲治暴力犯罪分子<br />\n<br />\n唔會出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫你地自己打撚夠佢"},{"pid":"50140548f63d76d042b080dabad149ca1cb44648","tid":1721080,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d0eb5c