，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是香港當前最緊迫的任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492242-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492242-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc60XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=23f3962b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492242-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=960105b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492242-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左見林鄭果次<br />\n今次係習近平第一次親自對抗爭表態</blockquote><br />\n推到有政要(Joshua Wong)講:我認同要向嚴重踐踏法治和社會秩序，嚴重破壞香港繁榮穩定，嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線嘅人處置，要止暴制亂、恢復秩序，所以啲人先要和平上街，依家係你逼人強硬，係咪你做錯？"}]}